erina Poggini, Claudio Mugnaini, Dario Shikhmiri, David Riondino, die fledermaus, Dielli Hoxha, Elisabetta Sepe, Eva Mei, Filippo Adami, Francesco Rizzi, Gabriele Spina, Gianni Paolo Mirenda, Il pipistrello, Isabella Messinese, Johann Strauss, Marina Comparato, Opera lirica, Paolo Ponziano Ciardi, Riccardo Massai, Teatro dell'Opera di Firenze"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/9ba640a7ac7b6985c46cf498c1470596" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Nicola-Lischi-116x150.jpg" width="77" height="100" alt="Nicola Lischi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Nicola Lischi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/nicola-lischi/">View all articles by Nicola Lischi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/02/lotello-di-fabrizio-monteverde-a-napoli-seduce-il-pubblico/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> L’Otello di Fabrizio Monteverde a Napoli seduce il pubblico</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/02/felice-romani-e-i-suoi-melodrammi-la-rosa-bianca-e-la-rosa-rossa-di-giovanni-simone-mayr/" rel="next">Felice Romani e i suoi melodrammi: &#8220;La rosa bianca e la rosa rossa&#8221; di Giovanni Simone Mayr <span class="meta-